==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: hominid
<hw>hominid</hw></mhw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>Any
animal of the family <fam>Hominidae</fam>, including modern man as well
as extinct species of the genera <gen>Homo</gen> and
<gen>Australopithecus</gen>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> homonid.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source> <source>+PJC</source>]</p>

